Directed by Fletcher Moules

Written by Kid Cudi. Kenya Barris. Ian Edelman. Maurice Williams. Esa Lewis. Sidney Schleiff. Judnick Mayard. Kid Cudi. Judnick Mayard. Sidney Schleiff

Star Kid Cudi(Jabari (voice) (as Scott Mescudi)). Jessica Williams(Meadow (voice)). Laura Harrier(Carmen (voice)). Ty Dolla $ign(Ky (voice)). Timothée Chalamet(Jimmy (voice)). Vanessa Hudgens(Karina (voice)). Christopher Abbott(Reed (voice)). Keith David(Mr. Rager (voice)). Arturo Castro(Len (voice)). Jaden Smith(Jordan (voice)). 070 Shake(Nadia (voice)). Macaulay Culkin(Downtown Pat (voice)). Maisha Mescudi(Ellie (voice)). Francesca Reale(Sydnie (voice)). Kerwin Frost(King of Hip (voice)). Teyana Taylor(Boxing Instructor (voice)). Kenya Barris(Moderator (voice)). Luis Guzmán(Huge Mover (voice)). Ian Edelman(Art Critic (voice)). Maurice Williams(Delivery Guy / Vagina Party Crasher (voice)). Fawn Stone(Dawn / Carmen’s Friend (voice)). Bill Lobley(Oleg / New Yorker / Taxi Driver (voice)). Montego Glover(Waitress / Pedestrian / Drunk Girl (voice)). Washington Kirk(Derek / Local Newscaster (voice))

Language English

Producers Kenya Barris. Kid Cudi. Dennis Cummings. Ian Edelman. Esa Lewis. Karina Manashil. Mike Moon. Fletcher Moules. Michael Penketh. Nick Read. Maurice Williams

Production Double Negative (DNEG). Khalabo Ink Society. MAD SOLAR
